---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Knowledge Base | Sentinel Expertise">
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-6 container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="text-center mb-20 relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        Technical Sovereignty
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
        Enterprise-Grade <br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-indigo-400">
          Compliance Infrastructure
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Discover the foundational pillars of the Sentinel architecture, engineered for deterministic zero-egress validation and legally-binding audit immutability.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 2x2 Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10">
      
      <!-- Card A -->
      <a href="/methodology" class="bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-[2rem] hover:bg-white/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
            ⚡
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
             <span class="mono text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Latency: &lt; 0.25ms</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Zero-Egress WASM Engine</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Deterministic execution in isolated WebAssembly modules. Raw data never leaves the volatile memory of the Edge node (Frankfurt).
        </p>
        <span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          Explore Architecture &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card B -->
      <a href="/compliance#art-11" class="bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-[2rem] hover:bg-white/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
            🔒
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-pulse"></span>
             <span class="mono text-[10px] font-bold text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Status: Append-Only</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">D1 Ledger-Lock Immutability</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Secure logging on Cloudflare D1. Every audit trail receives a unique ID, becoming immutable and impossible to alter retroactively.
        </p>
        <span class="text-indigo-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          View Technical File Annex &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card C -->
      <a href="/legal/sovereignty" class="bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-[2rem] hover:bg-white/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
            🇪🇺
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
             <span class="mono text-[10px] font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Jurisdiction: EU-Only</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Data Sovereignty (EEUR-1)</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Infrastructure enforced through Regional Services. Data processing and storage are strictly limited to locations within the European Union (Frankfurt Hub).
        </p>
        <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          Legal Policy Documentation &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card D -->
      <a href="/compliance#art-13" class="bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-[2rem] hover:bg-white/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
            📜
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
             <span class="mono text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Standard: Compliance-Native</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">EU AI Act Art. 43 Alignment</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Automatic generation of the conformity certificate. Logical mapping of algorithmic decisions onto European transparency requirements.
        </p>
        <span class="text-blue-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          Map Legal Articles &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Card E (Honeypot) -->
      <a href="/security" class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-red-500/10 p-8 rounded-[2rem] hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-red-500/20 transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
            🪤
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"></span>
             <span class="mono text-[10px] font-bold text-red-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Security: Digital Tripwires</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Active Deception & Honeypotting</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-4">
          Reactive architecture with trap endpoints and encrypted Canary Tokens in the D1 database. Active monitoring of intrusion attempts triggers automatic isolation (Auto-Ban) of hostile IPs at the Edge level.
        </p>
        <span class="text-red-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          Protocol Security Whitepaper &rarr;
        </span>
      </a>

    </div>

    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class="fixed top-20 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
    <div class="fixed bottom-20 right-10 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
  </main>
</Layout>
